      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$16,900 - Honest fair-condition vehicle with visible wear inside and out, but still a usable, decent driver overall. Expect cosmetic blemishes, age-related imperfections, and some deferred maintenance items rather than a clean, like-new presentation. The interior and exterior both show use, but it remains a reasonable option for someone looking for a more affordable vehicle and willing to accept normal wear and some needs that come with age.",
