    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Good-condition vehicle that has been well cared for and shows honest signs of normal use consistent with its age. The exterior presents nicely overall, with a solid finish and some minor cosmetic blemishes and light wear visible on closer inspection, but nothing that takes away from its overall clean appearance. The interior is also in good shape, with expected wear on commonly used surfaces, yet it remains clean, comfortable, and well kept. Overall, buyers can expect a dependable, presentable vehicle that is above average for its age, without being showroom perfect.",
      "price": 31900.0,
