    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$5,900 - Honest project classic with plenty of character and a great starting point for the right buyer. This is a poor-condition car that shows heavy age and wear, and it will need meaningful cosmetic, mechanical, and/or restoration work before it can be considered a dependable driver. That said, it\u2019s an affordable entry into classic ownership for someone who wants a car to tinker with, improve, or restore over time.",
