    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Honest, budget-friendly transportation with plenty of upside for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone who values affordability and sees the opportunity in a practical project, spare vehicle, or economical runabout. Priced to move and presented with transparency, it offers a straightforward path into ownership without a big upfront cost.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s seen some life but still has plenty to offer the right buyer. It\u2019s being sold in poor condition, so please don\u2019t expect a showroom example\u2014but if you\u2019re after an affordable runabout, a project, or something for parts, this could be a great fit. A straightforward, budget-friendly option from a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Straightforward, mechanically honest driver with plenty of life left for someone who wants dependable transportation or a solid project platform. Shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but the powertrain pulls well, the chassis feels composed, and it remains an easy, serviceable car to own. A good fit for a commuter, first car, or weekend wrenching candidate with strong value in the bones. Priced to move for someone who recognizes a practical, budget-friendly setup with real usability.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Starts, runs, gets you there. Not pretty, priced to move fast. Great beater, work car, or backup. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with honest, road-worn character and plenty of story left to tell. It has the kind of presence that makes it feel like a faithful old companion\u2014ready to be a dependable errand-runner, a budget-friendly project, or simply a practical set of wheels for someone who appreciates value over flash. There\u2019s real charm here for the right buyer: a vehicle that invites a little vision and rewards someone looking for affordable transportation with personality.",
      "price": 5200.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
